<Story_Main>
<resolution_title>Instruction to Corporate Secretary</resolution_title>
<basic_para><?= data.company.roles.corporate_secretary[0].name ?>
<?= data.company.roles.corporate_secretary[0].address ?>

</basic_para>
<chapter_header override="startParagraph=StartParagraph.ANYWHERE">Allotment of <?= data.security_type_long ?></chapter_header>
<para_1>Regarding the allotment of shares to the <?= plural(data.parties.new_investor, "new investor") ?> <?= commaAnd(data.parties.new_investor.map(function(p){return p.name})) ?>,</para_1>
<numbered_1_para>We hereby confirm that:</numbered_1_para>

<numbered_2_para>the Company's <?= plural(data.parties.new_investor, "allotment") ?>
 of <?= data._total_new_shares ?> RCPS <?= plural_verb(data.parties.new_investor, "is") ?>
 for cash consideration;
subscription monies amounting to <?= data._total_commitment ?> have been received by the Company in respect of the allotment of <?= data._total_new_shares ?> RCPS in the capital of the Company; and
we have established the identity of the new <?= plural(data.parties.new_investor, "investor") ?>, <?= commaAnd(data.parties.new_investor.map(function(p){return p.name})) ?>
and confirm that all is in order. </numbered_2_para>

<numbered_1_para>Kindly proceed with the lodgment of the returns on allotment of shares with the <?= data.company.roles.state_regulator[0].name ?>.</numbered_1_para>

<numbered_1_para>Kindly also issue the share certificates to the <?= plural(data.parties.new_investor, "investor") ?>.</numbered_1_para>

<para_1>Yours faithfully,</para_1>
